      <title>迪纳波利称纽约市交通资本升级面临 270 亿美元的缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/nyc-transit-capital-upgrades-face-27-billion-gap-dinapoli-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据纽约审计长的一份报告，美国最大的公共交通系统在下一份资本预算中可能面临 270 亿美元的资金缺口，这些资金将用于更换数千辆火车车厢、加强系统抵御极端天气的能力并提高可达性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/nyc-transit-capital-upgrades-face-27-billion-gap-dinapoli-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国预测机构警告称，到 2070 年代中期，公共债务将增长近三倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/uk-forecaster-warns-public-debt-will-nearly-triple-by-mid-2070s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国官方预测机构警告称，由于公共财政受到医疗费用和利息成本飙升的重创，政府债务在未来50年内将增长近两倍，达到GDP的270%以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/uk-forecaster-warns-public-debt-will-nearly-triple-by-mid-2070s</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 08:56:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施普林格·自然集团启动法兰克福 IPO，为上市再添新动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/springer-nature-starts-frankfurt-ipo-in-fresh-push-to-go-public</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权支持的学术出版商施普林格·自然 (Springer Nature) 计划在法兰克福进行首次公开​​募股 (IPO)，这将成为今年下半年欧洲第一家大规模上市企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/springer-nature-starts-frankfurt-ipo-in-fresh-push-to-go-public</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 08:53:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称德国商业银行可能只是欧洲银行并购的开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/commerzbank-may-just-be-start-of-european-bank-m-a-analyst-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 的分析师表示，德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 可能被意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 收购，这可能会引发欧洲银行业更多并购活动，从而推高被视为收购目标的银行的股票估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/commerzbank-may-just-be-start-of-european-bank-m-a-analyst-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 08:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国计划于 3 月份解除对所有股票的卖空禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/south-korea-aims-to-end-short-selling-ban-on-all-stocks-in-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构表示，计划在 3 月底解除卖空禁令，并将确保届时完成必要的规则修订。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/south-korea-aims-to-end-short-selling-ban-on-all-stocks-in-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>John Lewis 削减亏损，Waitrose 销售额反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/john-lewis-cuts-losses-as-waitrose-recovers-from-it-glitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于旗下高档连锁杂货店 Waitrose 的销售额回升，John Lewis Partnership Plc 的亏损有所收窄，这是 Sharon White 将权力移交给新董事长之前的最后一份业绩报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/john-lewis-cuts-losses-as-waitrose-recovers-from-it-glitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 06:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的矿工阻碍了南非股市的上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/struggling-miners-put-the-brakes-on-south-africa-s-stock-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市在新兴市场股市中处于领先地位，但来自中国的低迷消息可能会给关键的采矿业带来压力，并阻碍其优异表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/struggling-miners-put-the-brakes-on-south-africa-s-stock-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 05:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEEFA 称欧洲液化天然气产量达到峰值，搁浅资产风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/europe-at-peak-lng-heightens-risk-of-stranded-assets-ieefa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家能源智库表示，欧洲液化天然气消费量可能已达到峰值，但仍在继续建设进口终端和相关基础设施，这增加了这些工程闲置并成为搁浅资产的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/europe-at-peak-lng-heightens-risk-of-stranded-assets-ieefa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将降息但仍对未来路径持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/ecb-interest-rates-decision-lagarde-to-cut-but-stay-guarded-on-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将再次下调利率，但由于通胀尚未完全得到抑制，其对进一步行动的速度和程度仍守口如瓶。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/ecb-interest-rates-decision-lagarde-to-cut-but-stay-guarded-on-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
